<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head><meta charset="utf-8" /><title>Your Ticket</title>
<style>
body{font-family:-apple-system,sans-serif;background:#f5f5f5;margin:0;padding:0}
.container{max-width:560px;margin:40px auto;background:#fff;border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden}
.header{background:#1a1a2e;padding:32px;text-align:center}
.header h1{color:#fff;margin:0;font-size:22px}.header p{color:#a0aec0;margin:8px 0 0;font-size:14px}
.body{padding:32px}.body p{color:#4a5568;line-height:1.6;margin:0 0 16px}
.ticket{border:2px dashed #667eea;border-radius:12px;padding:24px;margin:24px 0;text-align:center}
.ticket .ref{font-size:24px;font-weight:700;color:#2d3748;letter-spacing:2px;margin:0 0 8px}
.ticket .event{font-size:18px;font-weight:600;color:#667eea;margin:0 0 16px}
.ticket .meta{font-size:14px;color:#718096;margin:4px 0}
.qr{margin:20px 0}
.qr img{border-radius:8px;max-width:200px}
.footer{background:#f7fafc;padding:20px 32px;text-align:center}
.footer p{color:#a0aec0;font-size:12px;margin:0}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
  <div class="header"><h1>Your Ticket</h1><p>Keep this safe — you'll need it at the event</p></div>
  <div class="body">
    <p>Hi {{name}}, you're all set! Here's your ticket for <strong>{{eventTitle}}</strong>.</p>
    <div class="ticket">
      <p class="ref">{{ticketRef}}</p>
      <p class="event">{{eventTitle}}</p>
      <p class="meta">{{formatDate eventDate}}</p>
      <p class="meta">{{eventVenue}}, {{eventCity}}</p>
      <div class="qr"><img src="{{qrCodeUrl}}" alt="QR Code" /></div>
      <p class="meta">Show this QR code at the entrance</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="footer"><p>Eventful — Your passport to unforgettable moments.</p></div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
